    event:
      "<p>I got my first computer and learned about programming. fell in love with 🤓 HTML & CSS</p>",
  },
  {
    title: "Work, Nav 2018",
    event:
      "<p>Earned my life's first money by developing a website in HTML & CSS for our local restaurant <a href='https://www.zomato.com/jaipur/cnf-cheese-fries-vaishali-nagar' class='text-blue-500 no-underline'>CNF</a> </p>",
