  {
    title: "Education, Jan 2020",
    event:
      "<p>Started learning programming in C in pandamic 🧑🏻‍💻 all thanks to <a href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/shubham-kumar-007959b5/' class='text-blue-500 no-underline'>my mentor</a> who help me on every step.</p>",
