  {
    title: "Work, Dec 2020",
    event:
      "<p>Found my life's first freelancing <a href='/projects/theperfumeyard/' class='text-blue-500 no-underline'>Ecom</a> project 🤝. developed in Wordpress and PHP</p>",
  },
  {
    title: "Education, Jul 2020",
    event:
      "<p>Started learning Full stack web & development, created <a href='/projects/firstly' class='text-blue-500 no-underline'>Firstly</a> and mastered React. </p>",
  },
  {
    title: "Education, Aug 2021",
    event:
      "<p>Explored many different technologies. created <a href='/projects/goldenblush' class='text-blue-500 no-underline'>Golden Blush</a> Started my <a href='https://youtube.com/@gxanshu' class='text-blue-500 no-underline'>YouTube channel</a> and Developed <a href='/notes/migrating-from-nextjs-to-astro-how-i-created-a-amazing-static-website/' class='text-blue-500 no-underline'>my site</a> with Hugo </p>",
